survey_response.review_text: Very friendly environment and the clinic is well maintained specially when it comes to cleanliness and values the time with proper guidance.

Dr.Kiran is an excellent professional Dentist who understands the root cause of the problem post which he plans the treatment. I had postponed consulting a doctor for more than 2 years having no hopes with the Dentists I previously visited and the traumatic explanations they gave me for the issue I consulted for.
Dr.Kiran on the other hand told me that it was no big deal and conducted the procedure on the very second day post consultation. Post undergoing the procedure I had no issues the very same day. It was indeed a big miracle and my family was quite shocked at the outcome. Highly recommend him for people who fear visiting a dentist, he would make your life so much so earlier and also super light on your pocket.
I was amazed at his consultation and procedure charges. It's hard to believe, that we can still avail quality services at such economical rates.

I visited dental frames with a badly infected tooth that was extremely painful. I was in my first trimester and therefore, required unsurpassed advice, which wouldn't hamper my well being. Dr. Kiran offered to perform an RCT, taking all the precautions as I was pregnant. He ensured to make the procedure as painless as possible, while constantly checking of i was at ease. He prescribed mild medication and completed the entire procedure in 2 sittings. I'm glad to be rid of the pain and did not experience any kind of pains after the procedure. I highly recommend the doctor and his clinic, which is equipped with extremely hygienic tools and machines.

I being a very sensitive person towards injections, low tolerance to pain landed at Dental Frames as per my friends suggestion due to tooth pain in my lower molar tooth. 
Dr.Kiran Raj, understood my problems, he listened to the problem one by one, made a note of them, asked me various questions , interacted well with a smiling face. He even convinced me that Root canal treatments are pain free and made me feel confident to go ahead for the root canal treatment . The myth and scaredness​ of injections were broken then day Dr.Kiran Raj started RCT treatment on my tooth. He administered anesthesia injection painlessly, RCT was done in 2 visits, he explained me each procedures step by step, shows me the X-rays, showed me all the sterilized files and instrument he used. And I got my cosmetic zirconia crown/ cap also done from him. I would recommend Dr.Kiran to all. ** ** ********** *** **** ******* *** *** ** *

My root canal treatment was done here.  There was no waiting as I went per scheduled appointment time. Dr. Kiran Raj is very thorough  with his job and ensures that the work done is perfect. I am satisfied with my results and will surely recommend him to anybody looking for dental treatments.
